longName: NorCom Information Technology GmbH & Co. KGaA
longBusinessSummary: NorCom Information Technology GmbH & Co. KGaA develops and implements big data solutions in Germany and internationally. The company offers DaSense, an AI-supported data management platform that combines data management with data analysis. It serves the public sector, media, and industrial companies. The company was founded in 1989 and is based in Munich, Germany.
